column5: Was a great day and the weather was fantastic.Congrats to all the winnersSpecial thanks to Harvey for putting on such a great event and all the volunteers. Collin came in first place, Collin has fished this derby every year and has won 3 times in the top 5, he sure has the technique down pat.Collin took home $450.00  Other top 5 winners     I actually won 2nd. $240.00 Few pictures of the anglers.
Great to see Dave.. looks like your buying the next round at the GTG this year LOL
Congrats on the win looks like it was a great day for all.  It creeps me out to see open water in November. LOL, wheres the ice???  besides in the cooler
Thanks Guys Was hoping to see a Quinte report on here. Leaving this morning for 3 days.
Congrats on 2nd place and good luck on Quinte!
